WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Congratulations! You have successfully completed the Forklift Operator Certification Course.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
You have demonstrated your understanding of forklift safety procedures,
proper inspection techniques, and safe operating practices.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Your certification shows that you are trained in compliance with
OSHA 29 CFR 1910.178 standards for powered industrial truck operations.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Remember, your employer will conduct a practical evaluation
of your operating skills in your specific workplace environment.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
This certification is valid for three years from the date of completion.
Refresher training may be required based on your workplace policies.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Always prioritize safety, conduct daily inspections,
and report any equipment defects immediately.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Your commitment to safety protects you, your coworkers,
and helps maintain a safe working environment.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Thank you for completing this training.
Continue to operate safely every day. 